# Final Recommendation

To reach launch readiness:

1. Implement token-based design system
2. Reduce fonts to two maximum
3. Refactor mobile dashboard layout
4. Unify aesthetic across marketing and app
5. Control copper usage strategically

Do this, and AutoMate transitions from:
‚ÄúCool startup project‚Äù

to

‚ÄúVenture-backable automotive infrastructure platform.‚Äù

